      • getCellularSphere

        public static ExplicitCellStream getCellularSphere(int dimension)
        This function returns a cell decomposition of the n-sphere. The decomposition contains 1 n-cell with its boundary glued to a single point.
        Parameters:
        dimension - the dimension of the sphere to produce
        Returns:
        a cellular sphere of the specified dimension
